<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">خَمْسَة وَثَمَانُونَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> عَن ابْن عمر:</span> الَّذِي تفوته الْعَصْر.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢ - لَا يتحَرَّى أحدكُم طُلُوع الشَّمْس.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣ - كَانُوا يَتَوَضَّئُونَ الرِّجَال وَالنِّسَاء.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤ - مثل أَصْحَاب الْقُرْآن مثل الْإِبِل.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٥ - صَلَاة اللَّيْل مثنى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٦ - وَعَن حَفْصَة إِذا سكت الْمُؤَذّن صلى رَكْعَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٧ - صَلَاة الْجَمَاعَة تفضل الْفَذ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٨ - صلوا فِي الرّحال.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>